{"tid":147864,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"拉莫斯指如果聽日巴塞出局我會更高興","createTime":"2017-03-08T07:17:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T01:00:00.000Z","uid":18279,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c9b6a989ac563e347d77ab92732a767ab451f63f","tid":147864,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T07:17:44.000Z","msg":"皇馬清風送爽下又晉一級，拉莫斯自2014年歐聯決賽後已攻入21球，當中有18球更是在球隊和波及輸波時攻入，這名關鍵先生賽後便說：「最重要是保持樂觀及積極，比賽一切都會有轉機。」他更補充指：「<span style=\"color: red;\">如果聽日巴塞出局，我會更高興</span>。」值得一提的是，皇馬各項賽事42場中，有33場最少失一球，其防守依然存在進步空間。<br />\n<br />\n垃圾拉膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bc1cba958bbfcf6d7e7e87ab27418c17de55b78","tid":147864,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T07:29:39.000Z","msg":"同國光榮牙"},{"pid":"98b81349b2957ba37e87f490aa1a76debe373021","tid":147864,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T07:31:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同國光榮牙</blockquote><br />\n唔同民族"},{"pid":"9e9874429349280a8974c1d639e006c460b8cf5e","tid":147864,"uid":14089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T22:32:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b537ccacf41c8e432a1a90757a4b08a837e0eb55","tid":147864,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T22:34:02.000Z","msg":"柒頭拉膠"},{"pid":"7dc8e638e910b160c187c93d0e68dc7b786d954b","tid":147864,"uid":1349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T00:57:22.000Z","msg":"蝗狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7562bd24e357abe527e099ac3c9ee0